{"type":"message","id":"15c6a69c","parentId":"24574163","timestamp":"2026-05-03T07:26:52.603Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'd be happy to help!\n\nTo get your OpenClaw project and all its files onto GitHub, I'll walk you through the steps. Please follow along:\n\n1. **Create a new repository**: Go to [GitHub.com](https://github.com) and sign in if you haven't already. Click the \"+\" button in the top right corner of the page, then select \"New\" from the dropdown menu.\n2. **Choose a repository name**: Enter a name for your OpenClaw project (e.g., \"OpenClaw-Assistant\"). Make sure it's unique and easy to remember.\n3. **Create a new repository**: Click the \"Create repository\" button.\n\n**Initial commit**\n\n1. **Initialize a local Git repository**: In your terminal, navigate to the directory where you want to store your OpenClaw project files (e.g., `cd /path/to/OpenClaw`).\n2. **Create a new folder for the repository**: Create a new folder named after your chosen repository name (e.g., \"OpenClaw-Assistant\").\n3. **Add all files from the current directory**: Run the command `git init` to initialize a local Git repository.\n4. **Add and commit all files**: Run the command `git add . && git commit -m \"Initial commit of OpenClaw project\"`.\n\n**Pushing changes to GitHub**\n\n1. **Link your local repository to GitHub**: Run the command `git remote add origin https://github.com/your-username/OpenClaw-Assistant.git` (replace `your-username` with your actual GitHub username).\n2. **Push changes to GitHub**: Run the command `git push -u origin master`.\n\n**Verify on GitHub**\n\n1. **Visit your GitHub repository**: Go to your GitHub dashboard and find your newly created repository.\n2. **Verify files are uploaded**: Make sure all files from your OpenClaw project are visible in the repository's file list.\n\nThat's it! Your OpenClaw project should now be hosted on GitHub. If you need help with any of these steps or have further questions, feel free to ask."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"llama3:latest","usage":{"input":4096,"output":432,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":4528,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1777793212601}}
