{"type":"message","id":"bd5c790d","parentId":"a728a7b2","timestamp":"2026-05-03T07:29:44.240Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"As a paid subscriber of OpenClaw, you already have access to the OpenClaw platform and its features.\n\nRegarding your question: Yes, you can use your ChatGPT Plus subscription with OpenClaw! Since OpenClaw is designed to work seamlessly with various AI models, including LLaMA (the model used by ChatGPT), you can integrate your ChatGPT Plus subscription into OpenClaw to utilize its capabilities.\n\nTo do so:\n\n1. Sign in to your OpenClaw account and navigate to the \"Settings\" or \"Preferences\" section.\n2. Look for the \"AI Model\" or \"LLaMA\" setting and select your ChatGPT Plus subscription as the preferred model.\n3. Adjust any settings specific to your ChatGPT Plus plan, such as adjusting the model's temperature or streamlining its output.\n\nBy integrating your ChatGPT Plus subscription with OpenClaw, you'll be able to take advantage of advanced AI capabilities within the OpenClaw environment, including:\n\n* Enhanced language understanding and generation\n* Improved conversational flow and context maintenance\n* Ability to fine-tune the model's performance based on user feedback\n\nFeel free to experiment and explore the possibilities!"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"llama3:latest","usage":{"input":4096,"output":245,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":4341,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1777793384239}}
