{"type":"message","id":"9db7daf3","parentId":"c828eb4c","timestamp":"2026-05-03T07:33:22.401Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"While OpenClaw is designed to work seamlessly with ChatGPT (or any other large language model), there are some limitations and considerations to keep in mind:\n\n1. **Concurrency**: When running multiple conversations or tasks simultaneously, OpenClaw might need to handle the increased load. This can lead to occasional delays or slower response times.\n2. **Memory and Resources**: As you scale up your usage, you may encounter memory or resource-related issues (e.g., out-of-memory errors). Be mindful of your system's specifications and adjust as needed.\n3. **Model Updates**: ChatGPT models are continuously updated and improved. OpenClaw will need to be updated accordingly to ensure compatibility with the latest model versions.\n4. **Data Storage**: As you generate and store more conversations, data storage limitations may arise. Make sure your system has sufficient disk space and consider implementing a database or caching solution to optimize performance.\n5. **Security and Confidentiality**: When using ChatGPT with OpenClaw, ensure that sensitive information is properly handled and secured. This includes storing conversation history securely, protecting user identities, and adhering to applicable data privacy regulations.\n6. **API Rate Limitations**: Be aware of the API rate limits set by Meta AI (the provider of ChatGPT). Exceeding these limits can result in errors or temporary account suspension. You can adjust your usage patterns or explore alternative models if you encounter issues.\n7. **Model Performance Variance**: As with any AI model, performance can vary depending on factors like input quality, topic complexity, and context. Be prepared to adapt and fine-tune your interactions as needed.\n\nTo mitigate these limitations, consider the following best practices:\n\n* Monitor system resources and adjust usage accordingly.\n* Implement caching or database solutions to optimize data storage.\n* Use secure protocols for storing and transmitting sensitive information.\n* Stay up-to-date with ChatGPT model updates and OpenClaw releases.\n* Be mindful of API rate limits and adjust your usage patterns as needed.\n\nBy understanding these limitations and implementing best practices, you can effectively use ChatGPT with OpenClaw to build powerful AI-powered tools."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"llama3:latest","usage":{"input":4096,"output":433,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":4529,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1777793602400}}
